Impact

Prompt injection through third-party content

Unauthorized execution of sensitive actions

Data leakage

Manipulation of AI responses

Abuse of integrated backend tools

Remediation

Treat all external content as untrusted.

Isolate retrieved content from system prompts.

Restrict tool execution based on user authorization rather than model output.

Implement prompt injection detection and filtering.

Require explicit user confirmation before executing sensitive actions.